  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <div type="mūlam" rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="TNV19">
<l>varuneṟi niṉaintu vāra leṉṟaluṅ</l>
<l>kāppiṭai yīṭṭiṟ kaiyaṟu kiḷaviyum</l>
<l>varuka veṉṟalum vāra leṉṟalum</l>
<l>paṭaittu moḻitaluṅ kuṭittiṟaṅ kūṟalu</l>
<l>marivaiyai yiṉṟiyā ṉaṟintē ṉeṉṟalō</l>
<l>ṭuriyaṉa kiḷanta piṟavun tokaii</l>
<l>varaivu kaṭāta lāku meṉmaṉār.</l></lg>
</div>
</body>
</text>
<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition" corresp="#Ed">
    <body>
      <head xml:lang="en">Commentary</head>
      <p xml:id="TNV19comm1">eṉpatu varaivu kaṭātal ām āṟuṇarttutaṉutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p xml:lang="en">The quoted [<hi rend="italic">cūttiram</hi>] intends to make known the way in which 
      'asking for marriage' occurs.</p> 
    <p xml:id="TNV19comm2">āṟu pārttuṟṟa vaccak kiḷaviyum varavu vilakkaluṅ kāppiṉ iraṅkiya kaiyaṟu 
    kiḷaviyum iraviṉum pakaliṉum nīvā veṉṟalum vāral eṉṟalum paṭaittu moḻitaluṅ kuṭit tiṟaṅ 
    kūṟalumāṉiṭa makaḷ ātal iṉṟaṟintēṉ eṉṟalum eṉa viṉṉa vellām varaivu kaṭātal eṉṟu colluvar pulavar eṉṟa vāṟu.</p>
    <p xml:lang="en">The speech situation of experiencing fear having seen the path; averting the coming; 
    the speech situation of desolation on account of the guarding; saying ‘you come either in the day or night’; 
    saying ‘do not come’ and saying ‘I knew this woman as being honouratble today’ - the poet-scholars say 
    all of these such [situations] are ‘asking for marriage’.</p>      
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem1"> 
        <l>āṟē yariya veṉṉā yāṟē</l>
        <l>malkupuṉal parantu kalluyarn taṉavē</l>
        <l>yiraviṉ varuvarnaṅ kātala</l>
        <l>ruravēṉ ṟōḻiyā ṉuyirvāḻ vēṉē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu1">eṉpatu āṟu pārttuṟṟa accak kiḷavi.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem2"> 
        <l>vārā tīmō cāra ṉāṭa</l>
        <l>vuṟupuli koṉṟa ciṟukaṇ yāṉai</l>
        <l>yāṟukaṭi koḷḷu maruñcuram</l>
        <l>mūṟu tuṭaiya tamiyai nīyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu2">eṉpatu varavu vilakkiṟṟu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem3"> 
        <l>yāyē tuyiṉmaṟan taṉaḷē yāyiṉu</l>
        <l>nāyu mūru naṉituñ calavē</l>
        <l>kāva lāḷa rataṉiṉun tuyilā</l>
        <l>rāykatir matiyaniṉ ṟalarum</l>
        <l>yāva tāṅko lēntiḻai nilaiyē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu3">eṉpatu kāppiṉ iraṅkik kaiyaṟu kiḷavi.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem4"> 
        <l>pakalē variṉu māṟṟāḷ pakaliṉ</l>
        <l>ṟiraviṉ variṉu mannilai yiṉaḷē</l>
        <l>viraicēr mārpa ceytiṟam viḷampē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu4">eṉpatu iraviṉum pakaliṉum nīvā veṉṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem5"> 
        <l>murukaṟ cevviyoṭu pakalvari ṉivvaḻi</l>
        <l>viraviyaṟ kavvai yañcutu</l>
        <l>miruḷvari ṉataṉiṉum peritañ cutumē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu5">eṉpatu iraviṉum pakaliṉum vāral eṉṟatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem6"> 
        <l>kaḻippūṅ kāṉa livvaḻi nerunal</l>
        <l>vaḻippaṭarn tuṇṭōr tēreṉa</l>
        <l>vaḻittu nōkkiṉa ḷemmaṉai peritē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu6">eṉpatu tōḻi paṭaittu moḻintatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem7"> 
        <l>kaḻaikeḻu cilampi ṉaruvi yāṭu</l>
        <l>maḻaimata yāṉaiyoṭu piṭikaṇ</l>
        <l>ṭuḻaikeḻu nōkki yuṉṉiṉaḷ peritē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu7">ituvum atu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem8"> 
        <l>varaital vēṭṭaṉi rāyiṟ pativayi</l>
        <l>ṉetirkoḷ cevviya remarē yivvayiṉ</l>
        <l>naṟunutaṟ peruntōṭ pētaiyuñ</l>
        <l>ciṟukuṭik kāṉavaṉ perumaṭa makaḷē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu8">eṉpatu kuṭit tiṟaṅ kūṟiyatu.</p>
</div>
<div type="citation" rend="parallel">
    <lg xml:id="TNV19poem9"> 
        <l>itaṟkoṇ ṭiṉiyān terinatu mēṉāḷ</l>
        <l>matikkō ṭuriñcu mālvarai vāḻkkaik</l>
        <l>kaṭavu ḷāka vallatu</l>
        <l>maṭavaraṉ mātarai matittaṉṟō vilamē</l>
    </lg>
</div>
<div type="koḷu" rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="TNV19koḷu9">eṉpatu iṉṟaṟintēṉ eṉṟal.<note> 19.</note></p>
</div>
